.form-group
  %label.control-label{for: "hoc-user-type"}=hoc_s(:signup_census_user_type)
  %div
    %select#hoc-event-type.form-control{name: "event_type_s", type: "select", required: true}
      %option{value: nil, selected: true}
      -['Teacher', 'Administrator', 'Parent', 'Student'].each do |event_type|
        %option{value: event_type}= event_type

.form-group
  %label.control-label{for: "hoc-user-type"}
    Who participates in an Hour of Code at this school?
  %div
    %select#hoc-event-type.form-control{name: "event_type_s", type: "select", required: true}
      %option{value: nil, selected: true}
      -['A few students', 'Some students', 'Most students', 'Nearly every student'].each do |event_type|
        %option{value: event_type}= event_type

.form-group
  %label.control-label{for: "hoc-user-type"}
    Beyond Hour of Code, how are students exposed to computer programming at this school?
  %br
    Computer programming, in this context, means topics such as algorithms, data structures and logic (like conditionals and loops). For these questions, do NOT include HTML/CSS, Web design, or how to use apps as "programming".
  %br
  %br
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    After school club
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    At least 10 hours of programming integrated into another course ( for example computer programming is taught in a science, math, techology etc. course)
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    Semester or year-long course that includes at least 20 hours of programming
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    This school teaches less than 10 hours of computer programming, but does teach another technology topics. (For example, learning to use applications, computer literacy, web design, history of computers, or other).
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    I don't know.
    
-# If they check the semester/year course.
.form-group
  %label.control-label
    Your school offers semester or year long computer science classes!

.form-group
  %label
    This course is:
    %div
      %input{name: "required-optional", value: "required", type: "radio", required: true}
        Required for students
      %input{name: "required-optional", value: "optional", type: "radio", required: true, style:"margin-left: 20px;"}
        Optional for students

.form-group
  %label
    How often is this course taught?
    %div
      %select#hoc-event-type.form-control{name: "event_type_s", type: "select", required: true}
        %option{value: nil, selected: true}
        -['< 1 hour per week', '1-3 hours per week', '3+ hours a week', 'I do not know'].each do |event_type|
          %option{value: event_type}= event_type

.form-group
  %label
    What topics does this course include?
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    Block-based programming
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    Text-based programming, such as JavaScript, Python, C++, etc.
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    Phyical computing/robotics
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    Internet and networking
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    Cybersecurity
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    Data Analysis
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    Web design using HTML or CSS
  %div
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "checkbox", value: "1"}/
    Game design using game layout tools without coding or programming
  %div
    Other:
    %input#hoc-match-volunteer-flag{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "text"}
  %br
  %br

    .form-group
      %label.control-label{for: "hoc-event-location"}
      Please tell us more about this class.
      %div
        %textarea#hoc-event-location.form-control{name: "match_volunteer_flag_b", type: "text", placeholder: "For example, name of the class, how often it meets, description of what is taught.", style:"height: 4em;"}
